snippet.textDisplay: i always get depressed with this song by Tufail Niazi with its intense emotional trance... but when my sister got married and all people were gather at hall and for some reason i had to return back home to pick something,there was no one in the house except for 2 of my relatives and they played this song on the tape and that moment the hidden pain and emotion in the song ifelt revealed to me that i never knew before!!! and listening this song again has taken me back to that very moment....  Anwar Maqsood Nasrii bayan couldnt be this better than Tufail Niazi singing.Great peace of melody!!!
